   "cell_type": "code",

   "source": [
    "def update_phi_GS_SOR(phi, N, omega):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Update NxN grid of phi using SOR and Gauss-Seidel\n",
    "    Inputs:\n",
    "    phi    potential\n",
    "    N      grid size\n",
    "    omega  SOR parameter\n",
    "    Outputs:\n",
    "    Updated phi \"\"\" \n",
    "    for i in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "        for j in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "            phi[i,j] = (1.0+omega)*0.25*(phi[i-1,j] + phi[i+1,j] + phi[i,j-1] + phi[i,j+1]) - omega*phi[i,j]\n",
    "    return phi"
   ]
  },
  {

    "## Question 1(c)"

   "source": [
    "tol = 1e-4\n",
    "delta = 1.0\n",
    "iter = 1\n",
    "omega = 0.7\n",
    "while delta > tol and iter<2000:\n",
    "    phiin = np.copy(phi)\n",
    "    phi = update_phi_GS_SOR(phi,N,omega)\n",
    "    phi[20:80,20] = 1.0\n",
    "    phi[20:80,80] = -1.0\n",
    "    phi[0,:] = 0.0\n",
    "    phi[-1,:] = 0.0\n",
    "    phi[:,0] = 0.0\n",
    "    phi[:,-1] = 0.0\n",
    "    delta = np.max(np.abs(phiin - phi))\n",
    "    iter += 1\n",
    "print(\"Finished after \",iter,\" iterations\")\n",
    "if iter >= 2000:\n",
    "    print(\"Failed to converge\")"
   ]

    "def explicit_2D_wave_eq_update(theta_n, theta_nm1,r):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Update wave equation using simple finite difference \n",
    "    approach.  Assumes periodic boundary conditions.\n",
    "    Inputs: \n",
    "    theta_n   Wave at time t_n     = n*dt\n",
    "    theta_nm1 Wave at time t_{n-1} = (n-1)*dt\n",
    "    r         Constant (c dt/dx)**2\n",
    "    Output:\n",
    "    theta at time t_{n+1} = (n+1)*dt \"\"\"\n",
    "    theta_np1 = 2.0*theta_n - theta_nm1 + r*r*(np.roll(theta_n,1,axis=0) - \n",
    "                                               2.0*theta_n + np.roll(theta_n,-1,axis=0) \n",
    "                                              ) + r*r*(np.roll(theta_n,1,axis=1) - \n",
    "                                               2.0*theta_n + np.roll(theta_n,-1,axis=1) )\n",
    "    return theta_np1"
   ]
  },

    "wavelength = 1 #m\n",
    "wavevector = 2*np.pi/wavelength\n",

    "\n",
    "# Define number of points\n",

    "# Initialise\n",

    "Q2_x = np.arange(0,3*wavelength,dx)\n",
    "Q2_y = np.arange(0,3*wavelength,dx)\n",
    "Q2_x2d, Q2_y2d = np.meshgrid(Q2_x,Q2_y)"
   ]

    "def calc_M(N,zeta,V,dt):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Calculate matrix M for Crank-Nicolson solution of TDSE\n",
    "    Inputs: \n",
    "    N    size of matrix\n",
    "    zeta parameter\n",
    "    V    potential (array)\n",
    "    dt   time step\n",
    "    Outputs:\n",
    "    (NxN) matrix\"\"\"\n",
    "    output = np.diag(2j*dt*V)\n",
    "    #output = np.zeros((N,N),dtype=complex)\n",
    "    stencil = np.array([-1j*zeta, 2.0*(2.0+1j*zeta),-1j*zeta])\n",
    "    for i in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "        output[i,i-1:i+2] += stencil\n",
    "        #output[i,i] += 2j*dt*V[i]\n",
    "    output[0,0:2] += stencil[1:3]\n",
    "    output[N-1,N-2:N] += stencil[0:2]\n",
    "    #output[0,0] += 2j*dt*V[0]\n",
    "    #output[N-1,N-1] -= 2j*dt*V[-1]\n",
    "    return output"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 16,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def calc_N(N,zeta,V,dt):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Calculate matrix N for Crank-Nicolson solution of TDSE\n",
    "    Inputs: \n",
    "    N    size of matrix\n",
    "    zeta parameter\n",
    "    V    potential (array)\n",
    "    dt   time step\n",
    "    Outputs:\n",
    "    (NxN) matrix\"\"\"\n",
    "    output = np.diag(-2j*dt*V)\n",
    "    #output = np.zeros((N,N),dtype=complex)\n",
    "    stencil = np.array([1j*zeta, 2.0*(2.0-1j*zeta),1j*zeta])\n",
    "    for i in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "        output[i,i-1:i+2] += stencil\n",
    "        #output[i,i] -= 2j*dt*V[i]\n",
    "    output[0,0:2] += stencil[1:3]\n",
    "    output[N-1,N-2:N] += stencil[0:2]\n",
    "    #output[0,0] -= 2j*dt*V[0]\n",
    "    #output[N-1,N-1] -= 2j*dt*V[-1]\n",
    "    return output"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "Nx = 401\n",
    "x = np.linspace(-100,100.0,Nx) # Lambda is 10\n",
    "k = 1.0\n",
    "sigma = 10.0\n",
    "x0 = 0.0\n",
    "psi0 = np.exp(-(x-x0)**2/(sigma**2))\n",
    "alpha = 5e-4\n",
    "V = alpha*x*x\n",
    "dx = 0.5\n",
    "dt = 0.1\n",
    "omega = 1.0\n",
    "zeta = dt/dx**2\n",
    "matM = calc_M(Nx,zeta,V,dt)\n",
    "matN = calc_N(Nx,zeta,V,dt)\n",
    "matMinv = np.linalg.inv(matM)\n",
    "b = np.zeros(Nx,dtype=complex)\n",
    "t = 0\n",
    "matMinvN = np.dot(matMinv,matN)\n",
    "matMinvb = np.dot(matMinv,b)\n",
    "plt.plot(x,psi0.real)\n",
    "plt.plot(x,V)"
   ]
